@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title NDP (IPv6): NS/NA + RS/RA (concept)

[Host IPv6] as H
[Router IPv6] as R
[Alt host] as H2

H --> R : RS (Router Solicitation)
R --> H : RA (Router Advertisement)\nprefix, gateway, flags

H -[#333333,dashed]-> H2 : NS (Neighbor Solicitation)\n(catre multicast)
H2 -[#333333,dashed]-> H : NA (Neighbor Advertisement)

note bottom
  NDP foloseste ICMPv6.
  Inlocuieste ARP + parte din configurare.
end note
@enduml
